## Meta-Cognitive Protocol

For EVERY phase below, apply this reasoning:

1. DECOMPOSE вҖ” break into 3-8 sub-problems
2. SOLVE вҖ” each piece separately, confidence score 0.0-1.0
3. VERIFY вҖ” logical consistency, factual grounding, completeness, hidden assumptions
4. SYNTHESIZE вҖ” combine using confidence scores as weights
5. REFLECT вҖ” if overall confidence < 0.8 вҶ’ identify weak points, retry that part
6. FINAL only when satisfied

